arStrings.szText: Harness the power of the enemy to face the hordes of Hell.

The Mother's Triune offer you power, believing you to be Sanctuary's last hope against the forces of Hatred.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}New Questline:{/c} Harness demonic power with with new character, Istel.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}New Dungeons - Hellbreaches:{/c} Hell itself is pulled into Sanctuary in these new risk/reward dungeons.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}The Infernal Hordes:{/c}  A new challenge awaits in World Tier 3! Face against the endless hordes of Hell.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}All new Season Journey:{/c} Conquer 7 Chapters of challenges.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}22 new Legendary Aspects & 10 new Unique Items:{/c} Explore new ways to build and play each Class.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}All new Cosmetics:{/c} Acquire seasonally themed looks in the Battle Pass and other new looks in the Shop.
